  "uid": "product-analytics",
  "title": "Analytics (Clickstream)",
  "description": "Unified clickstream dashboard (v4 Activity Register). TOP — product funnel over the ClickHouse events_resolved view (person_id = identified user if known, else anonymous): unique visitors, sessions, anon-vs-identified, pageviews, top clicks, time on page, and most-active users (anon included). BOTTOM ('Ingest pipeline (ops)') — the collector pipe itself from Prometheus: accept throughput (analytics_events_received_total), back-pressure drops when the in-process buffer is full (analytics_events_dropped_total), the resulting drop rate, and the writer's DB pool. Merged from the former 'Analytics Ingest (Clickstream Collector)' (uid analytics-ingest, now removed) on 2026-06-10.",
  "tags": ["analytics"],
  "time": {
    "from": "now-7d",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "refresh": "1m",
  "timezone": "",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 3,
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
        "uid": "aenigma-clickhouse"
      },
      "title": "Unique visitors",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
